General Information
===================

This package provides a Python interface to the GtkSheet widget set for GTK2.
Its home on the web is <http://github.com/vhernandez/pygtksheet>.

Victor M. Hern√°ndez-Rocamora <victor.hr@gmail.com>.

Installation
============

In the root directory of the distribution run the following commands in the
shell command line:

    ./configure
    make
    make install

See the file 'INSTALL' for a detailed explanation.

Documentation
=============

This package includes full library API documentation located in /docs. To 
generate documentation include the '--enable-docs' option when invoking
./configure script.

Also look at the examples included in the /examples directory.


